description.en-us: The Neon Speeders Series was introduced in 2023 as a semi-premium product line. All vehicles in this series feature special paint treatments that glow like neon lights under blacklight illumination. Most vehicles in this series are equipped with specially-designed NS6 plastic wheels; these are intended to resemble the Wal-Mart logo as the series is intended to be a Wal-Mart exclusive in the United States. While most vehicles have plastic chassis, starting in 2025, some models have been equipped with metal chassis, just like other semi-premium series.
